16:43.800 --> 16:45.900
The kids father is Lionel Canter.

16:46.300 --> 16:48.800
As in the inventor of surrogates, Lionel Canter.

16:51.800 --> 16:55.000
Jarid Canter,
son of Dr. Lionel Canter was found dead

16:55.300 --> 16:57.800
