22:19.000 --> 22:22.700
I can assure you VSI's products have the most
stringent safety standards in the industry.

22:23.200 --> 22:24.600
What about a human head?

22:25.700 --> 22:27.200
What would cause one of them to blow up?

22:27.900 --> 22:28.900
Agent Greer...

22:29.600 --> 22:30.300
We're not doctors.

22:31.400 --> 22:32.100
Honey...

22:32.500 --> 22:33.900
