23:09.200 --> 23:10.300
What are you doing?

23:26.000 --> 23:27.300
Mr. Steinberg?

23:28.700 --> 23:30.300
Seth Steinberg?

23:34.000 --> 23:34.800
Hello.

23:35.100 --> 23:36.000
