24:30.000 --> 24:32.700
No bullet holes?
No blast damage?

24:33.500 --> 24:35.800
No scratches.
No dirt. No mud.

24:36.400 --> 24:38.400
Mind if I check out the identity chip?

24:39.400 --> 24:41.000
