26:43.700 --> 26:45.400
Visual matching.

26:57.800 --> 27:00.500
- Cameras caught your guy.
- Where?

27:00.700 --> 27:02.700
Dorchester, Gore Park and Adams.

27:02.900 --> 27:04.500
Not far from the reservation.

27:04.800 --> 27:06.900
Boston PD is on its way.

27:07.500 --> 27:09.100
Stay here.
Keep tabs on him.

27:09.300 --> 27:10.800
Wait a minute where are you going?

27:11.100 --> 27:12.500
Dorchester.

27:13.600 --> 27:15.100
It wasn't too difficult.

27:15.200 --> 27:18.100
I put his face in the system and... Bingo!
We found him in an alley.

27:19.000 --> 27:21.200
K33 over there brought it to my attention.

27:21.500 --> 27:22.700
Thanks Jerry.

27:24.100 --> 27:25.700
He's one of our best watchers.

27:26.100 --> 27:27.400
He's semi-retired.

27:27.700 --> 27:29.800
So he gets to work out of
his beach house in Maine.

27:30.200 --> 27:32.600
- Pretty sweet huh?
- Yeah, it's a nice setup you have here.

27:33.100 --> 27:35.300
Yeah, we can access every
Surrie on the grid here.

27:36.300 --> 27:37.600
Touch a button.

27:38.100 --> 27:39.900
I can tap into anyone's feed.

27:40.600 --> 27:42.500
It's kinda like being inside Gods head.

27:44.300 --> 27:46.400
Ooooooh Boy... I felt that one coming.

27:47.600 --> 27:48.800
My name's Saunders by the way.

27:50.700 --> 27:52.000
Jennifer Peters.

27:52.600 --> 27:54.900
Yeah... Yeah you are aren't you?

27:56.300 --> 27:57.600
