42:53.000 --> 42:54.800
I'm not going home.

42:55.300 --> 42:57.500
Tom. We gotta forget the case.

42:58.000 --> 43:00.100
Stone is going to run things his way

43:00.300 --> 43:02.600
and as far as we're concerned, it's over.

43:02.800 --> 43:05.700
It's not over until we
get that weapon back.

43:07.800 --> 43:09.200
Then you gotta let me help you.

43:11.900 --> 43:14.000
I'm not gonna let you win.

43:14.200 --> 43:15.700
Take care of yourself Peters.

44:04.400 --> 44:07.200
Death came to Myles Strickland

44:08.600 --> 44:11.200
As death comes to all men.

44:12.400 --> 44:13.600
But for Myles

44:14.800 --> 44:16.300
It's not an ending.

44:17.800 --> 44:19.500
It's a new beginning.

44:21.400 --> 44:24.900
When you sacrifice your
own personal desires

44:26.900 --> 44:28.400
for a greater cause, a greater good.

44:30.000 --> 44:31.400
You never die.

44:32.700 --> 44:34.300
You never disappear.

44:35.500 --> 44:38.000
That is what it means to be human.

44:39.700 --> 44:41.300
There is no alternative

44:41.900 --> 44:44.700
You can try to escape by
living through a puppet

44:45.400 --> 44:47.100
Through a machine.

44:47.800 --> 44:51.800
But deep down inside, you
know you're living a lie

44:54.200 --> 44:56.400
Here, inside these walls

44:56.700 --> 44:58.500
We understand the truth.

45:05.000 --> 45:08.500
We sacrifice many modern
pleasures and conveniences

45:08.800 --> 45:10.900
to feel truly connected.

45:12.100 --> 45:13.500
Not with machines

45:16.100 --> 45:17.200
But with ourselves.

45:22.500 --> 45:24.400
This is the human condition.

45:24.800 --> 45:26.900
This is what gives life meaning.

45:27.900 --> 45:28.800
My friends.

45:29.200 --> 45:32.700
Soon the day will come
when surrogacy must end.

45:33.600 --> 45:35.500
That day, I promise you

45:36.200 --> 45:37.400
Is close at hand.

45:38.200 --> 45:41.000
The day... we get a second chance.

46:11.200 --> 46:12.300
Excuse me.

46:14.300 --> 46:15.600
- Can I help you?
- Yeah

46:15.900 --> 46:17.700
I'd like to speak to
The Prohet for a minute.

46:18.100 --> 46:19.500
You and everybody else bud, no.

