about Myles Strickland please?

46:30.800 --> 46:31.800
Enough.

46:35.400 --> 46:37.800
It's different when you actually feel the pain.

46:38.700 --> 46:39.500
Isn't it?

46:41.700 --> 46:43.300
What happened to Strickland?

46:45.400 --> 46:47.000
Was he a friend of yours?

46:47.600 --> 46:48.600
He had a weapon.

46:49.100 --> 46:50.800
A very dangerous weapon.

46:52.200 --> 46:54.600
My people will do
anything to get this back.

46:57.500 --> 47:01.900
Well... if I happen to come
across such a weapon

47:03.400 --> 47:06.000
