delivered to your door.

47:07.900 --> 47:09.600
Show him to the gates.

47:11.400 --> 47:12.400
Gently.

47:55.900 --> 47:57.000
Agent Greer.

47:57.600 --> 47:59.400
May I offer you a ride?

48:03.000 --> 48:04.800
You'll have to excuse my appearance.

48:05.200 --> 48:07.700
It's not safe for me to
use my usual surrogates.

48:09.400 --> 48:10.300
Dr. Canter.

48:10.400 --> 48:12.200
This is one of VSI's newer models.

48:13.300 --> 48:14.600
How long have you been following me?

48:14.800 --> 48:18.200
Long enough to know you're getting
nowhere solving my sons murder.

48:21.700 --> 48:23.300
You lost a child Agent Greer?

48:25.000 --> 48:25.700
How?

48:29.300 --> 48:30.800
Car accident.

48:35.900 --> 48:37.400
It was just an accident.

48:39.200 --> 48:40.200
I'm sorry.

48:45.200 --> 48:48.700
I can think of no worse tragedy
than a parent outliving a child.

48:53.400 --> 48:54.700
All I can tell you

48:56.200 --> 48:58.000
