48:58.800 --> 49:00.300
His name was Myles Strickland.

49:01.100 --> 49:02.600
Lived on the Res'.

49:04.600 --> 49:06.100
He was killed by his own people.

49:06.800 --> 49:07.700
And that's it?

49:08.300 --> 49:09.300
Case solved?

49:10.600 --> 49:12.700
One man didn't act on his own.

49:14.100 --> 49:15.500
Whatever killed my son

49:15.700 --> 49:18.700
was an extraordinary
sophisticated technology.

49:19.100 --> 49:21.500
Far beyond the capabilites of the Dreads.

49:22.200 --> 49:24.900
We're talking about a
billion dollar weapons project.

49:25.900 --> 49:28.100
Who do you know spends money like that?

49:38.300 --> 49:41.000
Focus on the weapon, where it came from.

49:58.400 --> 49:59.700
Mmmm do me.

50:05.900 --> 50:07.700
How was it?

50:18.000 --> 50:20.400
- Hey Maggie?
- No, thank you.

50:20.900 --> 50:22.700
Come on... it'll take the edge off.

50:32.100 --> 50:33.800
Tom?
Honey?

50:38.300 --> 50:39.900
