50:40.400 --> 50:41.100
Yeah...

50:42.200 --> 50:43.300
I can see that.

50:43.600 --> 50:44.800
What happened?

50:46.800 --> 50:50.100
Tom I don't want you going out
without your Surrie ever again.

50:50.300 --> 50:53.500
- Tom?
- You look very nice, Sexy.

50:53.800 --> 50:56.100
