51:10.100 --> 51:11.400
Okay go have a good time.

51:48.400 --> 51:49.800
Tom stop it!

52:11.700 --> 52:12.700
Tom?

52:13.800 --> 52:15.100
Tom, what was that?

52:17.100 --> 52:18.900
- What?
- What you want from me?

52:26.200 --> 52:27.300
I want you...

52:28.800 --> 52:30.100
...My wife.

52:31.800 --> 52:33.300
I am your wife.

52:33.400 --> 52:34.800
And you won't see it.

52:35.500 --> 52:36.500
No. God.

52:37.800 --> 52:38.600
No you're not.

52:41.600 --> 52:44.400
Not...
Not... this.

52:45.200 --> 52:47.600
Not this... thing...
This...

52:52.100 --> 52:53.300
I just want you.

52:55.200 --> 52:57.400
And I want the woman that's in that room.

52:57.700 --> 52:58.800
My wife.

53:03.100 --> 53:04.700
Things have changed Tom.

53:05.000 --> 53:07.000
You're... No you've changed.
You're just scared.

53:07.200 --> 53:09.200
You're just scared...
We could go talk to somebody...

53:10.400 --> 53:13.300
Maggie...
Maggie your my wife.

54:14.100 --> 54:16.700
Agent Greer?
