classified information... - I know where it is.

56:12.200 --> 56:13.100
Where is it?

56:14.200 --> 56:14.900
Right...

56:22.900 --> 56:24.300
Is called an O.D.

56:25.100 --> 56:26.600
Overload Device.

56:28.200 --> 56:31.000
The idea was to end
the battle with one shot.

56:32.400 --> 56:34.700
Giving the software virus straight to the CPU.

56:35.200 --> 56:37.100
Disables the Surries instantly.

56:37.700 --> 56:40.800
