defeat the built in failsafes.

56:42.300 --> 56:43.500
...kill the operators.

56:43.800 --> 56:45.100
Who makes it?

56:47.100 --> 56:48.200
VSI.

56:50.300 --> 56:51.400
After the test

56:53.100 --> 56:54.600
the project was scrapped.

56:55.700 --> 56:57.100
Every unit was destroyed.

56:57.700 --> 56:59.100
Except this one right?

57:02.000 --> 57:02.900
Where is it?

57:04.000 --> 57:05.900
Right now it's in the hands
of the Human Coalition.

57:06.000 --> 57:07.600
- How long have they had it?
- A day...

57:07.800 --> 57:09.000
Maybe two.

57:10.700 --> 57:12.100
This is out of your hands.

57:12.700 --> 57:14.400
Military will handle this.

57:22.200 --> 57:24.200
- You called for us?
- Take this to

57:24.600 --> 57:26.500
