57:27.600 --> 57:29.000
A woman will meet you there.

57:29.700 --> 57:31.600
Agent Jennifer Peters.

57:32.200 --> 57:35.100
You're to give it to her... and her alone.

57:43.400 --> 57:44.300
Peters.

57:45.300 --> 57:46.300
What are you doing?

57:47.100 --> 57:49.000
