58:58.100 --> 58:59.400
It's...
I just...

59:01.300 --> 59:02.600
I love you.

59:03.700 --> 59:06.400
I love this smart, beautiful

59:07.300 --> 59:09.100
Intelligent, funny

59:10.400 --> 59:11.500
Woman... And...

59:13.800 --> 59:15.000
I can't sleep.

59:16.600 --> 59:19.100
And when I do... I have these dreams that are...

59:25.000 --> 59:27.000
And I can't stop
thinking about him.

59:28.100 --> 59:29.800
Tom... don't...

59:30.500 --> 59:32.000
Don't you ever think about him?

59:32.900 --> 59:34.500
