she doesn't smile anymore.

59:45.000 --> 59:46.100
I don't believe that.

59:46.400 --> 59:48.900
The only reason I can get up in the
morning and get out of the house

59:49.100 --> 59:50.800
Is because THIS is who I am now.

59:51.100 --> 59:52.600
- That's okay, honey.
- No, no.

59:53.000 --> 59:54.500
- No. - Maggie. - NO!

59:55.100 --> 59:56.400
Maggie wait.

01:00:55.700 --> 01:00:58.700
Brothers and sisters gather
close and prepare yourselves.

01:00:59.600 --> 01:01:01.900
The day of the resurrection is upon us.

01:01:02.100 --> 01:01:05.800
The day we make history.
The day we launch the revolution!

01:01:12.900 --> 01:01:14.700
