Over there!

01:01:39.100 --> 01:01:43.600
- Cease fire! - Hands on your head. - Cease fire.

01:01:54.100 --> 01:01:55.100
My God.

01:02:19.900 --> 01:02:22.800
I couldn't figure out why
the cops let Strickland off.

01:02:23.400 --> 01:02:25.300
So I started going
through the payroll records.

01:02:26.700 --> 01:02:27.900
You won't believe this.

01:02:28.200 --> 01:02:30.500
- For the last 16 months...
- He was working for us.

01:02:31.000 --> 01:02:31.800
That's right.

01:02:32.900 --> 01:02:34.600
Which means Stones
gotta be dirty.

01:02:35.300 --> 01:02:37.900
Looks like he hired Strickland to kill Canter.

01:02:44.600 --> 01:02:46.700
Hey Tom.
I thought you were on leave?

01:02:47.300 --> 01:02:48.300
Oh yeah... I am.

01:02:49.200 --> 01:02:51.300
Actually I was just suspended.

01:02:51.800 --> 01:02:54.200
Another investigation,
I'll just clear my desk out.

01:02:54.400 --> 01:02:55.800
You should be home.

01:02:56.100 --> 01:02:57.600
Recuperating Ok?

01:02:57.900 --> 01:02:59.700
Not walking around here in the flesh...

01:03:00.200 --> 01:03:02.800
I was at home then I came
here to clean out my desk.

01:03:03.000 --> 01:03:05.600
And you know... before the
medication kicks in... Hopefully...

01:03:05.900 --> 01:03:09.800
I can find a box...
And... Oh...

01:03:10.900 --> 01:03:13.400
Victor Welsh wanted me to say hello.

01:03:14.600 --> 01:03:15.400
I'm sorry?

01:03:15.600 --> 01:03:17.800
Victor Welsh, VSI, the good looking kid?

01:03:18.000 --> 01:03:21.200
Very excited you coming over there, finally
moving into the private sector

01:03:21.400 --> 01:03:22.500
You must be excited.

01:03:23.000 --> 01:03:25.300
Why don't you come into my
office, you're not looking too sharp.

01:03:26.300 --> 01:03:27.600
Yeah Yeah... I got a minute.

01:03:29.300 --> 01:03:31.900
It's a good move for you.
It's a really good group over there.

01:03:32.600 --> 01:03:33.500
Smart.
Talented.

01:03:34.300 --> 01:03:35.700
Great legal department.

01:03:36.800 --> 01:03:38.400
Great working environment.

01:03:39.700 --> 01:03:43.000
You gotta be happy with those
first year stock options huh?

01:03:43.300 --> 01:03:44.900
What are you talkin' about?

01:03:46.000 --> 01:03:48.600
Myles Strickland, the guy I was chasing...

01:03:49.400 --> 01:03:51.400
The guy you hired to kill Canter.

01:03:51.600 --> 01:03:54.300
- Tom you got it all wrong.
- You gave him the weapon.

01:03:54.700 --> 01:03:56.000
VSI makes them.

01:03:56.300 --> 01:03:59.600
They give one to you, you give it to
Strickland so he can go out and kill Canter.

01:03:59.800 --> 01:04:02.000
The only problem is, he
killed his son by mistake.

01:04:02.300 --> 01:04:05.100
- Something is wrong with you.
- Why are you doing this?

01:04:06.400 --> 01:04:08.200
Money? Is that what it is?

01:04:08.900 --> 01:04:10.600
You need help.

01:05:06.500 --> 01:05:09.600
This is Stone. That son of a
bitch Greer disabled my unit!

01:05:09.900 --> 01:05:10.700
Stop him!

01:05:14.300 --> 01:05:15.400
Go... Go!

01:05:27.500 --> 01:05:30.300
Jesus. No wonder VSI
wants Canter dead.

01:05:30.800 --> 01:05:32.300
He's in bed with The Prophet.

01:05:32.900 --> 01:05:34.800
He's funding the
Anti-Surrogacy Movement.

01:05:35.300 --> 01:05:36.500
He's given them names.

01:05:36.900 --> 01:05:40.400
Crazy bastard invents surragotes and
does everything he can to destroy them.

01:05:41.100 --> 01:05:44.400
It doesn't connect Stone to the murder.
We need to link him to the weapon.

01:05:44.900 --> 01:05:46.500
He needed codes to use it.

01:05:46.900 --> 01:05:48.800
I want you to look for access codes.

01:05:50.100 --> 01:05:52.700
You get the codes... You nail Stone.

01:06:02.400 --> 01:06:04.600
Good job Agent Greer.
Thank you.

01:06:05.000 --> 01:06:07.400
This is Agent Peters. I found Greer.

01:06:07.600 --> 01:06:10.000
He's been in an accident at
Market and Hanover.

01:08:09.700 --> 01:08:12.100
- FBI!
- Get out of the car!

01:08:13.400 --> 01:08:14.400
He's gone.

01:08:14.600 --> 01:08:16.000
Scanning for identity chip.

01:08:16.200 --> 01:08:17.800
He doesn't have one, he's a meatbag!

01:08:18.000 --> 01:08:19.500
There's and exit in the back!

01:08:49.100 --> 01:08:50.800
Hey! Where you going?!
HEY!

01:08:55.000 --> 01:08:57.300
Bobby it's Greer.
I need a remote shutdown.

01:08:57.500 --> 01:08:59.500
Agent Peters has been hijacked.

01:08:59.800 --> 01:09:01.500
You gotta disconnect her.

01:09:02.300 --> 01:09:04.100
Bobby?
Hello Bobby?

01:09:04.399 --> 01:09:05.700
Peters.

01:09:06.700 --> 01:09:07.899
Have you gone insane?

01:09:08.300 --> 01:09:11.300
Why don't you put the gun down? huh?
What are you trying to prove?

01:09:12.100 --> 01:09:14.600
She's grabbing into the entire 3rd network!

01:09:26.700 --> 01:09:29.100
Maggie get offline right away, as
soon as you get this message.

01:09:29.700 --> 01:09:31.700
Something is going to
happen to the surrogates.

01:09:33.000 --> 01:09:36.200
- She'll only speak to you sir. - Why don't
you just move in and take her down huh?

01:09:37.000 --> 01:09:38.300
She has a human hostage.

01:09:39.899 --> 01:09:41.399
Uh... the slob Saunders...

01:09:52.700 --> 01:09:53.500
Peters?

01:10:00.600 --> 01:10:02.500
Peters it's me Andy Stone.

01:10:03.300 --> 01:10:04.800
That's far enough Stone.

01:10:08.400 --> 01:10:10.200
I know who hired you to kill me.

01:10:12.000 --> 01:10:15.300
I hope my old partners
at VSI paid you well.

01:10:16.800 --> 01:10:21.200
Did you feel even a second of remorse when
you found out you murdered an innocent boy?

01:10:22.500 --> 01:10:23.400
Canter?

01:10:25.000 --> 01:10:26.200
I don't believe it.

01:10:27.200 --> 01:10:31.000
Ok... How about you tell me something Doctor.
Huh?

01:10:31.800 --> 01:10:33.800
What did you expect VSI to do?

01:10:34.200 --> 01:10:37.100
Just stand by while you tore
down everything they built?

01:10:37.500 --> 01:10:39.600
You left us no choice
but to take you out.

01:10:40.500 --> 01:10:43.700
You created the technology, you changed
the world and now want to destroy it?

01:10:44.800 --> 01:10:45.600
So what?

01:10:46.700 --> 01:10:48.000
So you can take us backwards?

01:10:49.100 --> 01:10:50.900
So we can all live like Dreads?

01:10:54.700 --> 01:10:56.600
So we can live like
human beings.

01:10:59.100 --> 01:11:00.100
Really Doctor?

01:11:01.400 --> 01:11:03.300
You should learn
how to live with your regrets.

01:11:05.500 --> 01:11:06.700
Now give me the gun.

01:11:34.000 --> 01:11:35.600
That's for my son.

01:11:49.100 --> 01:11:50.600
I need to see your boss.

01:11:50.800 --> 01:11:52.500
I need to see Dr. Canter right away!

01:11:52.700 --> 01:11:55.100
Oh good... Listen to me... I
gotta to see your boss. Dr. Canter he...

01:12:07.600 --> 01:12:09.100
Device connected.

01:12:14.300 --> 01:12:16.100
Over here officers, this way.

01:12:36.600 --> 01:12:39.100
<i>Warning! Commencing Upload.</i>

01:14:20.500 --> 01:14:21.600
Hello Tom.

01:14:25.400 --> 01:14:27.100
Nice to finally meet you.

01:14:28.000 --> 01:14:29.000
In the flesh.

01:14:36.300 --> 01:14:39.200
Now... Lie on the floor, face down.

01:14:41.800 --> 01:14:44.600
It's a little different when you have
to kill somebody with your own hands.

01:14:45.800 --> 01:14:48.700
You're going to have to squeeze the trigger.
You don't have a machine to do your dirty work.

01:14:51.000 --> 01:14:52.100
Feel that?

01:14:53.200 --> 01:14:55.600
An accelerated pulse, the
heightened awareness...

01:14:56.200 --> 01:14:58.400
Savouring each breath
as if it were your last.

01:14:59.000 --> 01:15:00.200
That what you've been missing.

01:15:01.000 --> 01:15:02.400
That's what everbodys been missing.

01:15:02.700 --> 01:15:07.000
- So you kill millions of people?
- I changed the course of human
history when I invented surrogates.

01:15:08.700 --> 01:15:10.300
Now I'm going to change it back.

01:15:10.900 --> 01:15:12.600
You can't change what's been done.

01:15:14.200 --> 01:15:16.000
You and I know that
better than most people.

01:15:17.200 --> 01:15:19.900
My son's death will not
have been in vain.

01:15:21.200 --> 01:15:23.100
Not if it heals mankind.

01:15:24.300 --> 01:15:25.300
Heals mankind?

01:15:26.600 --> 01:15:28.700
That what you want to do?
You want to kill everyone?

01:15:29.200 --> 01:15:31.800
- And that's going to heal mankind?
- They're already dead.

01:15:32.000 --> 01:15:34.200
They died the minute they
plugged into those machines.

01:15:34.400 --> 01:15:35.600
This is not the solution.

01:15:35.900 --> 01:15:37.900
- That's the way it is.
- That's not the way it is!

01:15:38.100 --> 01:15:41.000
I had a vision. I was going
to empower the powerless.

01:15:41.700 --> 01:15:44.300
To enable other like me to walk, to feel.

01:15:45.100 --> 01:15:49.100
- To live a normal life.
- Listen to me! They're going to call you
a murderer! That is what you're doing!

01:15:49.300 --> 01:15:51.000
Surrogacy is a perversion.

01:15:51.400 --> 01:15:52.600
It's an addiction.

01:15:52.800 --> 01:15:55.700
And you have to kill the
addict to kill the addiction.

01:15:57.000 --> 01:15:58.700
<i>Upload Complete.</i>

01:15:58.900 --> 01:16:01.500
You're too late.
What I've done can't be stopped.

01:16:01.900 --> 01:16:03.600
Now you're going to be witness

01:16:04.900 --> 01:16:06.600
to the rebirth of humanity.

01:16:07.800 --> 01:16:09.500
That's my gift to you.

01:16:10.700 --> 01:16:12.000
No! NO!

01:16:37.100 --> 01:16:39.000
<i>Selecting All Surrogates.</i>

01:16:39.900 --> 01:16:41.300
How do we make it stop?

01:16:44.000 --> 01:16:46.200
Bobby it's Greer.
Tom Greer.

01:16:46.700 --> 01:16:48.600
How do we shut
this thing down?

01:16:50.500 --> 01:16:52.300
<i>All Database Selected.</i>

01:16:53.700 --> 01:16:56.000
Jesus... He's trying to kill everyone.

01:16:56.800 --> 01:17:01.800
Listen... That thing has just uploaded
a virus into the system that's going to
kill anyone who's using a surrogate.

01:17:02.500 --> 01:17:03.700
It's already started.

01:17:04.000 --> 01:17:07.100
Bobby we need to
unplug everyone... Now!

01:17:08.000 --> 01:17:09.000
Think!

01:17:09.500 --> 01:17:12.100
Uh.... Uh....

01:17:14.700 --> 01:17:17.100
I... Ok... Move over to
the terminal on the left!

01:17:17.600 --> 01:17:19.600
RED253

01:17:20.100 --> 01:17:23.200
We can't unplug them
but maybe we can buffer the operators.

01:17:24.600 --> 01:17:26.600
Oh God... Ok... we've got 10 seconds!

01:17:30.600 --> 01:17:31.900
Ok look... there are three passes.

01:17:32.300 --> 01:17:33.900
Type in Tango in the first.

01:17:34.000 --> 01:17:35.400
Xray in the second.

01:17:35.500 --> 01:17:37.200
772 in the third.

01:17:37.300 --> 01:17:38.300
Hit Enter.

01:17:41.600 --> 01:17:44.100
HIT ENTER! What
happe... Ah.. Shit!

01:17:44.400 --> 01:17:46.800
SHIFT and Enter!
SHIFT and Enter!

01:17:49.400 --> 01:17:51.500
Uh... Ah...

01:17:54.700 --> 01:17:57.200
Uh... You just saved about
billion lives there.

01:17:59.900 --> 01:18:02.400
Ok... Now we gotta keep
the surrogates from getting fried.

01:18:02.600 --> 01:18:04.600
Please go back to the first
terminal hit the Enter key.

01:18:05.400 --> 01:18:07.100
Hit the Enter key please!

01:18:08.300 --> 01:18:10.500
Good... Now press Yes.

01:18:16.200 --> 01:18:17.300
So that's it?

01:18:17.700 --> 01:18:19.000
Everyone's safe?

01:18:19.100 --> 01:18:20.400
- What?
- All the people?

01:18:20.600 --> 01:18:23.300
Yes... Yes... Of course yes.
All the operators are safe.

01:18:23.500 --> 01:18:26.700
But if you don't press abort, all the
surrogates are going to be destroyed.

01:18:30.100 --> 01:18:32.400
We don't have a lot
of time man... Hit Yes.

01:18:33.500 --> 01:18:35.600
Hi? Hello? Hit Yes Greer!

01:18:37.300 --> 01:18:39.000
Greer I'm talking
about ALL the surrogates!

01:18:50.200 --> 01:18:51.400
Wha... What are you doing?

01:18:53.600 --> 01:18:54.500
Greer?!

01:18:54.900 --> 01:18:56.900
For God's sakes what
are you waiting for?!

01:18:57.100 --> 01:18:58.600
Press the friggin' button damnit!

01:18:59.100 --> 01:19:00.200
Freeze!

01:19:34.000 --> 01:19:35.600
<i>Transmit Complete.</i>

01:21:48.100 --> 01:21:49.000
Excuse me.

01:23:20.200 --> 01:23:24.300
<i>Bare with us as we're still trying to piece
together exactly what has occured today</i>

01:23:24.700 --> 01:23:28.300
<i>There has been a total systems
failure of the central surrogate grid</i>

01:23:28.700 --> 01:23:33.300
<i>In every major city on the eastern
seaboard, possibly in the entire United States...</i>

01:23:33.700 --> 01:23:37.400
<i>...describing an identical failure
in those cities this is unbelievable...</i>

01:23:37.600 --> 01:23:39.200
<i>...no reports of human casualties</i>

01:23:39.600 --> 01:23:42.500
<i>the damage appears limited
only to surrogate units...</i>

01:23:42.800 --> 01:23:46.400
<i>...thus far, no statements from VSI. They have
not responded to requests for information...</i>

01:23:46.700 --> 01:23:49.800
<i>...Paris, London, Beijing
all reporting the same thing...</i>

01:23:50.000 --> 01:23:54.700
<i>...there is still no official word when or
if surrogate services can be restored.</i>

01:23:55.500 --> 01:23:59.200
<i>It appears, at least for now,
that we are on our own.</i>

